	<key>readme</key>
	<string># Thesaurus.com Workflow for Alfred

A fast, zero-dependency Alfred Workflow that retrieves synonyms and antonyms directly from Thesaurus.com.

## Keywords
- `syn {word}` : Search for synonyms.
- `ant {word}` : Search for antonyms (you can also simply type `syn {word} ant`).
*(You can customize these triggers in the workflow configuration!)*

## Modifiers
- `↵` : Copy synonym to clipboard. If Auto-paste is enabled, instantly pastes the word.
- `⌘ + ↵` : Open the synonym directly on Thesaurus.com.
- `⇧ + ↵` : Jump down the rabbit hole and instantly search for synonyms of the selected word.
</string>
